 <label>Table 3</label>
 <caption>
  <title>
   <italic>In Vitro</italic> and 
   <italic>in Vivo</italic> Antiviral Activity of Some Potential Compounds against CoVs, Including SARS-CoV-2
  </title>
 </caption>
 <table frame="hsides" rules="groups" border="0">
  <colgroup>
   <col align="left"/>
   <col align="left"/>
   <col align="left"/>
   <col align="left"/>
